      • isValid

        public static boolean isValid(double side1,
                              double side2,
                              double side3)
        Returns if the specified sides can form a triangle.

        If any sides are less than or equal to 0.0, the triangle will default to be invalid.

        Parameters:
        side1 - first side of the triangle
        side2 - second side of the triangle
        side3 - third side of the triangle
        Returns:
        true if the specified sides can form a triangle. Otherwise, false.

      • area

        public static double area(double side1,
                          double side2,

        Returns the area of the triangle with the specified sides.

        If any sides are less than or equal to 0.0, the area will default to 0.0.

        Parameters:
        side1 - first side of the triangle
        side2 - second side of the triangle
        side3 - third side of the triangle
        Returns:
        the area of the triangle
